org.pikater.web.experiment.server

Class BoxInfoServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pikater.web.experiment.server.BoxInfoServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBoxInfoCommon<java.lang.Integer>

    public class BoxInfoServer
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBoxInfoCommon<java.lang.Integer>

    The server's notion of "boxes". This format is intermediate. The following chain explains the conversion cycle:

    (BoxInfoClient - user's browser) <-> (BoxInfoServer - web application server) <- (AgentInfo - core system)
    Author:
    SkyCrawl
